===// Client to the TGTP server //===

*) Compile

$> make

It requires the BOOST library (property_tree)

*) No instalation required

*) Use (the "gentzen.mat.uc.pt" is an experimental server, it will be
 updated to a diferente server later on) 

$> client gentzen.mat.uc.pt 2093 <query>

where <query> should be, the SQL part of the WHERE clause

-) look for a conjecture name, notice the ' '

--) look for the simple word (e.g. 'teoName LIKE "%ceva%"')

--) a simple (one line only) string (e.g. 'teoName  LIKE "%ceva%theorem%"'

-) a query and filters (e.g. 'teoName LIKE "%ceva%" AND proverId=2')

2 | GCLC Area Method             | 9.00
4 | COQareaMethod                | 1.0  
5 | GCLC Wu Method               | 9.00 
6 | GCLC Groebner Basis Method   | 9.00 
7 | GDDM-TPTP-FOF                | 1   


for more information about this last option contact the autors

*) More information

See the code "client.cpp" for more information about the information
received from the server. 


Pedro Quaresma (pedro@mat.uc.pt)